title: How to Use God's Promises! Pack of Bible verses to overcome!
description:
Hi! Here I bring you a pack of Key Bible Verses (and a guide to help you use them) that will make you FREE, HEALTHY, PROSPEROUS, HAPPY, FULFILLED and most importantly: will teach you to HEAR GOD yourself. 

This is nothing new, people have decreed Gods promises for thousands of years, since the end of all things is near you have to prepared because nothing will be enough to survive except walking close to God. If you are atheist, just keep these files just in case. Bye
